    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are honored to present this exemplary automotive specimen, preserved in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle represents the zenith of its production year, boasting an unblemished exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously curated and subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection, its mechanical performance is as flawless as its aesthetic presentation. This is a rare acquisition opportunity for the professional who demands uncompromising quality and distinction.",
